  <data name="label18.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Instead of showing the common samples, this app can be also started as a RenderForm sample.
To do that, open the program.cs file, comment the definition of SamplesForm (line 17) and 
uncomment the code to start RenderFormSample (lines 20 and 21).
The RenderFormSample can run at as many frames per second as possible.
</value>
